    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Zachary sets the scene with his poem, “A Dispensation For The Dispensationalists”."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Dr. Daniel Hummel is the Director for University Engagement at Upper House, a Christian study center serving the University of Wisconsin-Madison. Daniel is the author of "
        },
        {
          "text": "The Rise and Fall of Dispensationalism: How the Evangelical Battle Over the End Times Shaped a Nation",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "text": "Covenant Brothers: Evangelicals, Jews, and U.S.-Israeli Relations",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": ". Daniel has written about religion, politics, and foreign policy for the "
        },
        {
          "text": "Washington Post, Christianity Today",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": ", and "
        },
        {
          "text": "Religion News Service",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
